the region is also expected to feature prominently in the prime
minister's discussions with the president."
</P>
<P>
The Vietnamese leader is also scheduled to address leading
Malaysian businessmen at a luncheon to be organized by the
Malaysian National Chamber of Commerce and Industry. 
