denounced separatist activities by the Dalai Lama and called for
taking a firm stand against separatism.
</P>
<P>
Ginzom Gyincainpuncog, vice-chairman of the Tibet Regional
Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference (CPPCC), said the Dalai Lama has never stopped
attempting to split China by plotting and stirring up troubles in
Tibet in collaboration with international forces hostile to China.
</P>
