million shares traded, industrial 10.915 million shares,
construction 21.948 million shares, trading/services 38.811
million shares, infrastructure projects 598,000 shares, finance
24.526 million shares, hotels 672,000 shares, properties 18.865
million shares, plantations 7.658 million shares, mining 953,000
shares, trusts 179,000 shares and loans 27.871 million shares.
