<HEADLINE> Iran Welcomes Development in Tajikistan, Sierra </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, March 12 (Xinhua) -- Iran has expressed welcome to the
latest development in Tajikistan and Sierra Leone, Iran's official
news agency IRNA reported on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Iranian Foreign Ministry spokesman Mahmoud Mohammadi Wednesday
night hailed the appointment of Haji Akbar Turajonzoda first
deputy prime minister of Tajikistan as a practical step toward
peace in the country.
</P>
<P>
