<HEADLINE> Business Rising at Shanghai's Hongqiao International Airport </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, March 12 (Xinhua) -- Hongqiao International Airport
in Shanghai served 13.27 million passengers last year, up 7.5
percent over 1996.
</P>
<P>
