<HEADLINE> Chinese Aircraft Maintenance Company Wins International Award </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 12 (Xinhua) -- The Beijing-based Aircraft
Maintenance and Engineering Corp. (AMECO) was recently honored
with the Flight International Aerospace Industry Award for its
achievements in the international aircraft major maintenance and
modification market in 1997.
</P>
