<HEADLINE> Chinese Foreign Minister Expects Closer Sino-Japanese Ties </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 12 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier and Foreign
Minister Qian Qichen told a press conference here today that the
