<HEADLINE> Qian: Arms Embargo May Be an Option on the Kosovo Issue </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"There are really too many weapons in that region," he said,
adding that when the turmoil erupted not long ago in Albania,
there was a very widespread disemination of weapons in this
region, and almost everybody has a weapon, which is very
dangerous.
</P>
<P>
The European Union is already prepared to impose an arms
embargo on this region, and the United Nations has not yet
discussed it. We believe that maybe the United Nations is not an
appropriate place for the discussion of this matter, because you
can imagine if arms embargo is only imposed on Yugoslavia, that
may not be able to resolve this matter totally.
</P>
<P>
