Council in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR),
which will be conducted in a fair, just and open manner.
</P>
<P>
In response to questions at press questions, Qian said the
coming May will see the election for the first legislative council
in Hong Kong. The method for the election has been formulated by
the SAR government, the election will be organized and run by the
SAR government, and all the preparations are underway.
</P>
