the CPPCC National Committee from the HKSAR have come to Beijing,
which demonstrates that the representatives from the HKSAR are
also in the position to participate in the discussions and
administration of the state affairs of the whole of China, he
noted. It is not that they have come to Beijing just for the
purpose of discussing affairs concerning the Hong Kong SAR.
</P>
<P>
