<HEADLINE> Gustafsson Cruises into Third Round </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, March 11 (Xinhua) -- Second-seeded Magnus Gustafsson
of Sweden sailed into the third round of the Copenhagen Open
tennis tournament in Copenhagen, denmark on Wednesday with a 6-2,
6-3 win over Renzo Furlan of Italy.
</P>
<P>
In another second-round match, Andrei Pavel of Romania beat
Tuomas Ketola of Finland 6-7 (4-7), 6-2, 6-1.
</P>
