Parer was forced to admit to the Senate Wednesday night that he
had breached pecuniary interest guidelines, or the ministerial
code of conduct, over his 1.3 million U.S. dollars investment in
coal shares, plunging the federal government into yet another
crisis.
</P>
<P>
