after the release of a report that recommends scrapping most of
Australia Post's monopoly over mail delivery.
</P>
<P>
The Australian Financial Review:
</P>
<P>
-- Ian Macfarlane, governor of the Reserve Bank of Australia,
has cautioned the International Monetary Fund against using its
role in the Asian economic crisis to force political change in the
region. 
